A healthy outside starts with a healthy inside. Step into your Nearest Fabcafe & enjoy our Healthy, Made #ALT, AltIngredients delicious platter.

To reserve a table, contact your nearest fabcafe: www.fabcafe.menu/storelocator (link in bio)

MEET OUR NEXT CHARTBUSTER! Take a bow, Mr. Chocolate Cake!

The melt-in-the-mouth Chocolate Cake at Fabcafe is such a sweet favourite from our menu. And with good reason too. It actually brings alive our innovative MADE#ALT approach to baking. 

We make our chocolacious bestseller of the most nutritious #Altingredients like almond flour and house-made chocolate sauce, coconut sugar and desi ghee. Yes, that’s right. No butter, refined grain, gluten or white sugar. So decadent, yet so very good for body, mind and soul.

Our new menu reflects the MADE#ALT principles that form the bedrock of the culinary experience we offer. Come over and we’ll take you through it.. Or visit fabcafe.menu for sheer bliss to be delivered to your doorstep!
....................

WANT A CRUNCH WITH EXTRA PUNCH? 😋

Say hello to the Super Nut n Seed Trail Crunch from Fabcafe. And goodbye to bad-for-you snacking!

A nutrient-dense Granola Mix with high protein seeds and nuts, this one packs in all the good stuff. It's Paleo friendly, vegan and completely free of grains and refined sugar. Told ya!

Get your resealable pouch from a Fabcafe outlet. And tell us how you like having it best. Any way is a good way!

The most fun thing to do when it's chilly is to dig into our pickled chillies! 🌶
 
Made out of fresh, natural ingredients in cold pressed mustard oil, Fabcafe Chilli Pickle is the zing thing for every meal!
 
So what's your favourite way to have our Chilli Pickle? Do you team it with stuffed parantha, or love it with dal chaawal? Tell us your way. Spice it up!

A bowl of our Ladakhi Thupka is like a warm hug from a long-lost buddy! Just the kind of comfort food you crave . Piping hot, absolutely healthy and so very delicious!

The broth is flavourful and wholesome, with Zucchini Noodles, juicy chicken chunks and lots of veggies. And because it's free of wheat and refined oil, it's so slurpworthy when you're a little under the weather. 

Try it and you'll swear by it. Whatever the season. Or reason.

Hey Delhi! 

Fabcafe has reopened!  And we are serving your faves, made to order, at Fabindia’s Experience Centre, Vasant Kunj with a fresh new vibe!

From wholesome salads and flavour-packed curries to sizzling chaats and aromatic biryanis — everything is crafted from scratch in our live kitchen, using responsibly sourced, fresh ingredients.

Come in, unwind, and savour healthy, delicious food made with love.

Open daily from 10 AM to 10 PM.
3rd Floor, Fabindia Experience Centre, Vasant Kunj

Your table’s waiting. And so are we.
Team Fabcafe
